---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const TEAL = '#05d7d1';
const GOLD = '#E8B84B';
---

<Layout
  title="About Theia | RGV Web Designer — Socially Awkward Media"
  description="Meet Theia Goodner — graphic designer since 2003, web designer since 2006, and the small-business champion behind Socially Awkward Media in Laguna Vista, TX."
  noMascot
>

  <!-- Banner -->
  <header class="about-banner">
    <p class="about-well" aria-hidden="true">Well,</p>
    <h1 class="about-heading">THIS IS AWKWARD</h1>
    <img
      src="/ollie-full-body.png"
      alt="Ollie the mascot"
      class="ollie"
    />
  </header>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-2xl px-6 pb-16">
    <div
      class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-white shadow-sm"
      style={`border: 2px solid ${TEAL};`}
    >
      <div class="h-2 w-full" style={`background-color: ${GOLD};`}></div>

      <div class="space-y-5 p-8 leading-relaxed text-neutral-800">
        <p class="text-lg font-bold">Some people stumble into creativity. Theia just never stumbled out.</p>

        <p>It started in 2003 with a spark for graphic design — the kind that quietly takes over your brain and never really lets go. By 2006 she'd added web design to the mix, because apparently one creative obsession wasn't enough.</p>

        <p>When Socially Awkward Media came to life in 2022, it didn't stay behind a screen for long. Theia took the brand into the community by organizing and hosting Small Business Saturday — a vendor event dedicated to spotlighting small and home-based businesses. For three years running, that event brought together 100+ vendors and real, enthusiastic community support. Because building up small businesses isn't just a service — it's something she genuinely believes in.</p>

        <p>Today, Socially Awkward Media is exactly where it's always been heading — helping your brand look as good as the work you do.</p>

        <p class="italic" style={`color: ${TEAL}; font-weight: 600;`}>
          No matter what stage of your project you're in — from idea spark to goal reached — you're in the right place.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-banner {
    position: relative;
    background-color: #05d7d1;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 30px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: visible;
  }
  .about-heading {
    font-family: 'Lilita One', cursive;
    color: #ffffff;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 12px #E8B84B;
    paint-order: stroke fill;
    font-size: 100px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .ollie {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 44px;
    height: 220px;
    width: auto;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .about-well {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    transform: rotate(-10deg);
    transform-origin: bottom left;
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 64px;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    z-index: 4;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
</style>
